## Eases Quick Reference
| Feel | Ease |
|------|------|
| Snappy UI | `power2.out` |
| Bouncy | `back.out(1.7)` |
| Elastic | `elastic.out(1, 0.3)` |
| Smooth scrub | `none` |
| Natural decel | `power3.out` |

